<subSubSection pageId="110" pageNumber="506" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="110.[1442,2648,288,641]" pageId="110" pageNumber="506">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1444,1800,446,479]" pageId="110" pageNumber="506">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List because there is no information available regarding extent of occurrence, area of occupancy, population size or population trends. No specific conservation measures are known to be in place for the Iranian White-toothed Shrew.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
